OL,6,BBegin your week by learning the truth  
OL,7,Bbehind the tabloid speculation about   
OL,8,Bthe loves and lives of the stars!      
OL,10,ETABLOID RUMOUR -BDenise Van Outen is   
OL,11,Bto star in a new TV sitcom, Babes In   
OL,12,BThe Wood, about a bunch of friends in  
OL,13,BLondon's trendy St John's Wood.        
OL,14,E(The Sun)                              
OL,16,ECLUB TRUTH -B"Yes, it's absolutely     
OL,17,Btrue," says Ms Van Outen's agent.      
OL,18,B"The Sun has got it right this time!"  
