OL,6,BClub's neverending battle against      
OL,7,Btabloid half-truths continues afresh!  
OL,9,ETABLOID RUMOUR -EBlack Grape singer    
OL,10,BShaun Ryder is writing a series of     
OL,11,Bfilms about guns, money and drugs.     
OL,12,E(The Mirror)                           
OL,14,ECLUB TRUTH -B"Yep, it's absolutely     
OL,15,Btrue," says a chipper press officer on 
OL,16,Bbehalf on Shaun. "I can't say too much 
OL,17,Bmore about it, but if you want to know 
OL,18,Bmore, you should read the Melody Maker 
OL,19,Btomorrow!"                             
