OL,6,BClub sifts the tattle from the truth!  
OL,7,B                                       
OL,8,ETABLOID RUMOUR -EThe Backstreet Boys   
OL,9,Bare set to become super rich after     
OL,10,Btying up a deal to star in their own TV
OL,11,Bshow. The boys will play themselves and
OL,12,Bare currently ironing out a deal with a
OL,13,BTV company.E(Daily Star)               
OL,15,ECLUB TRUTH -B"It's absolute hogwash!"  
OL,16,Bsays the Backstreet's PR. "That's the  
OL,17,BStar for you. I don't know where they  
OL,18,Bget them from!"                        
